$ HTML element: canvas

Draw graphics onto a HTML page with → development/languages/JavaScript.
-
There are two APIs with which graphics can be rendered onto a `<canvas>` element:
  • → https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API[Canvas API]
  • → https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API[WebGL API] (See also → development/web/WebGL)

